NAME
       _get-instance-install-dir - Returns the instance's install directory.

SYNOPSIS
           _get-instance-install-dir [--help]
           [--nodedir nodedir] [--node node]
           instance_name

DESCRIPTION
       The _get-instance-install-dir subcommand will return the instance's
       install directory.

OPTIONS
       --help, -?
           Displays the help text for the subcommand.

       --nodedir
           The directory where the instance's node is located.

OPERANDS
       instance_name
           The name of the instance.

EXAMPLES
       Example 1, Get instance's install directory in a custom node
       directory

           This example returns the install directory for the instance

               asadmin> _get-instance-install-dir --nodedir C:\workspace\testnode\ int1

EXIT STATUS
       0
           command executed successfully

       1
           error in executing the command

